  <brief_title>Calibration and Validation of Masimo's O3 Regional Oximetry Device in Neonates, Infants and Children</brief_title>
  <official_title>Calibration and Validation of Masimo's O3 Regional Oximetry Device in Neonates, Infants and Children Undergoing Cardiac Catherization</official_title>
